if(curr->right!=NULL)queue[rear++]=curr->right;
}
}
Iterative preorder/inorder(using an explicit stack instead of recursion) is a common follow-up (“can you
do it without recursion?”) — it works because it’s simulating exactly what the call stack was doing for you
automatically:
